Hi Steve,

the wav file has a cue list embedded into it, consisting of 72 cues - one for each allophone. If EVPmaker is set up to use the embedded cue list, the other settings such as Overlap, Zerocross, Crossfade, Segment size etc. don&#39;t apply, thus they will be greyed out. These options, and the &quot;Use Cue List&quot; option, exclude each other. If &quot;Use Cue List&quot; should be greyed out, then uncheck the other options.

Stefan

